'''Mohanad Mostafa Ahmed Abdelmonem Lasheen''' ({{langx|ar| مهند مصطفى أحمد عبد المنعم لاشين}}; born 29 May 1996) is an Egyptian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defensive midfielder]] for [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[Pyramids FC|Pyramids]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Egypt – Mohanad Mostafa Lasheen – Profile with news, career statistics and history – Soccerway|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/mohanad-mostafa-lasheen/491068/|website=us.soccerway.com|language=en}}</ref>

==Career==
In March 2016, Mostafa was promoted from youth team to first team in [[Ismaily SC|Ismaily]],<ref>{{cite web|title=القماش يقرر تصعيد 7 ناشئين للفريق لهذا السبب ! !|url=https://www.ismailyonline.com/article.php?id=3964|website=www.ismailyonline.com|accessdate=25 September 2017|language=ar}}</ref> but he moved six month later to Alassiouty (now is called pyramids) Sport in the [[Egyptian Second Division]] and signed a 2-year contract.<ref>{{cite web|title=بالصور.. الأسيوطي يضم "لاشين" الإسماعيلي|url=http://www.elbetelabyad.com/133938|website=البيت الأبيض|accessdate=25 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://sports.weladelbalad.com/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%B7%D9%89-%D9%8A%D8%AF%D8%B9%D9%85-%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%88%D9%81%D9%87-%D8%A8%D9%85%D9%87%D9%86%D8%AF-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B4%D9%8A%D9%86-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D8%A7/|title=الأسيوطى يدعم صفوفه بمهند لاشين لاعب الإسماعيلي السابق {{!}} استاد ولاد البلد|date=2016-09-10|work=استاد ولاد البلد|access-date=25 September 2017|language=ar-AR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.albawabhnews.com/2107927|title=مهند لاشين يوقع للأسيوطي سبورت|work=البوابة نيوز|access-date=25 September 2017}}</ref> Mostafa was part of the Alassiouty's (now is called pyramids) squad that promoted to [[2017–18 Egyptian Premier League]], he also scored the winning goal in the match that guaranteed the promotion for the club before 5 weeks from the end of the season.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.elfagr.org/2537367|title=لاشين : حسمنا الصعود للدوري الممتاز قبل 5 مباريات|work=بوابة الفجر|access-date=25 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.alqemanews.com/t~37999|title=حوار{{!}} مهند لاشين: بفضل الله وكابتن "أيمن" كنت صاحب هدف صعود الأسيوطي للممتاز {{!}} القمة نيوز|work=alqemanews.com|access-date=25 September 2017|language=ar}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.yallakora.com/ar/news/321286/|title=رسميا.. الأسيوطي أول المتأهلين للدوري الممتاز – ياللاكورة|access-date=25 September 2017}}</ref> In April 2017, Ismaily SC made negotiations with Alassiouty (now is called pyramids) to sign the player.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.innfrad.com/News/21/667376/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A5%D8%B3%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%8A%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B6-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%B7%D9%89-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%A9-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B4%D9%8A%D9%86-|title=الإسماعيلى يفاوض الأسيوطى لاستعادة "لاشين" – انفراد|date=30 April 2017|work=انفراد|access-date=25 September 2017|language=ar-Ar}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.youm7.com/story/2017/4/30/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A5%D8%B3%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%8A%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B6-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%B7%D9%89-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%A9-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B4%D9%8A%D9%86/3212221|title=الإسماعيلى يفاوض الأسيوطى لاستعادة "لاشين" – اليوم السابع|date=2017-04-30|work=اليوم السابع|access-date=25 September 2017|language=ar-Ar}}</ref>

==International career==

On 2 December 2025, Lasheen was called up to the Egypt squad for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cafonline.com/afcon2025/news/egypt-name-final-28-man-squad-for-totalenergies-caf-afcon-2025-salah-leads-pharaohs-charge/|title=Egypt name final 28-man squad for TotalEnergies CAF AFCON 2025, Salah leads Pharaohs' charge|publisher=[[Confederation of African Football]]|date=2 December 2025|access-date=12 December 2025}}</ref>

